{"id": 1695, "genre": 1001, "title": "在哪些情况下，你会选择抛弃一个品牌？", "description": "或者说，品牌做了什么事，会让你从此把它拉黑？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 8152, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170518143952ardWHzpCQEwFycTU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-19T03:00:48Z", "options": [{"id": 205312, "content": "根据自己对该品牌产品的价值评估，或者使用产品后出了让我不能接受的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008682}, {"id": 205568, "content": "质量下降，远不如从前", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249012}, {"id": 220160, "content": "越来越觉得难看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074340}, {"id": 352256, "content": "我个人倒是没有什么品牌爱好……好用就行。我这次买华为下次就可以小米，再下次三星，再下次魅族，都没问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 205313, "content": "大牌涨价抛弃了我", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261387}, {"id": 205569, "content": "产品频繁出问题+售后服务差", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749508}, {"id": 210177, "content": "外强中干", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038808}, {"id": 205314, "content": "性价比太高，太贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937096}, {"id": 205570, "content": "服务差\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789546}, {"id": 206338, "content": "当有了一个可以替代他的品牌后", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037652}, {"id": 205315, "content": "贵！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243294}, {"id": 205571, "content": "售后太恶心，推卸责任。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 54091}, {"id": 206083, "content": "电子产品又贵又烂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693824}, {"id": 205316, "content": "win10不支持前代机型", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986431}, {"id": 205572, "content": "突然降价，而且是全部商品，感觉掉分了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709210}, {"id": 207876, "content": "反华/认为顾客没有他们的产品就活不下去(爱买不买)的自以为是傲慢型", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147602}, {"id": 205317, "content": "不好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291456}, {"id": 205318, "content": "自从百度被爆各种负面事件之后，从此改用必应、谷歌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825428}, {"id": 205574, "content": "诚信，这是最基本的要求。\n价值观，这是品牌的要求。\n以上两点的变动 可以通过无数个侧面反应出来，过了阈值我就走", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036174}, {"id": 205319, "content": "小鲜肉代言", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243211}, {"id": 205575, "content": "颜值低俗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036176}, {"id": 205320, "content": "放弃原来的体育精神 向明星效应妥协 你们知道我在说谁的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721524}, {"id": 206601, "content": "死贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038173}, {"id": 229129, "content": "越来越不用心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101668}, {"id": 206090, "content": "性价比变低，产品感觉不对的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037162}, {"id": 228362, "content": "素质低下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589122}, {"id": 205323, "content": "政治不正确的，支持zd的，一知道马上不买，比如表脸的Lush", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772677}, {"id": 205579, "content": "性價比差，用低價品質賣高價", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036181}, {"id": 205324, "content": "质量下降，光环破裂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026165}, {"id": 205580, "content": "网易新闻 和凤凰新闻 从来没见过一家创办多年且专业的网络新闻媒体会用专题的形式去黑一个公众人物 感觉它已经失去了一个媒体应有的尊严", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745419}, {"id": 205325, "content": "宣传中医宣传很多玄学", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245984}, {"id": 205581, "content": "高价格，低配置。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036192}, {"id": 217101, "content": "一个广告连续播送三遍的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049258}, {"id": 205326, "content": "看见更好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035412}, {"id": 205582, "content": "设计变丑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922412}, {"id": 206606, "content": "质量与售后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038139}, {"id": 207886, "content": "你们(-｡-;....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989073}, {"id": 205327, "content": "增加了太多广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994919}, {"id": 205583, "content": "有过严重事故的品牌，例如 强生 三鹿 三星", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902558}, {"id": 205328, "content": "就没有选择品牌的权利。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004493}, {"id": 205584, "content": "产品品质下降，这是最基本的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016090}, {"id": 206096, "content": "实用性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035537}, {"id": 205329, "content": "产品广告毫无新意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586232}, {"id": 205585, "content": "打折促销", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588023}, {"id": 226833, "content": "关于一个快餐，自从我点了金针菇滑鸡，他混了点鸭肉之后。我就没再叫了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095555}, {"id": 206098, "content": "让我有了一拍即合的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017277}, {"id": 219154, "content": "在德克士喝冰可乐，冰块里冻住了n多苍蝇，从此不吃德克士。四川大学大北门外那家。好像关了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069993}, {"id": 252434, "content": "刷屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353006}, {"id": 205587, "content": "魅族做小而美时很喜欢，现在的战略越来越觉得它很烂，没有情操", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860738}, {"id": 205843, "content": "不走心都是设计，不一般的歧视", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697574}]}